<document xml:lang="sma">
   <header>
        <title>Installing, enabling and switching keyboards in macOS
        10.9-10.12</title>
   </header>
   <body>
       <p>To be able to write easily in Sámi, you should use a Sámi keyboard.
       Below you'll find instructions on how to download and install keyboards,
       enable them, and how to switch easily among the enabled keyboards.</p>
      <section>
        <title>Installation</title>
        <ol>
          <li>Go to the <a
            href="http://divvun.no/no/keyboards/desktopindex.html">Divvun
            keyboard download page</a>, and click on the
            <strong>download link for the keyboard installer</strong>:
            <p><img alt="Download installer"
            src="images/01-10.12-download-keyboard-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>Click on the <strong>Show downloads</strong> button, and then
            click on the <strong>Show in Finder</strong> button:
            <p><img alt="Show installer package in Finder"
            src="images/02-10.12-downloaded-keyboard-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>Double click the installer package:
            <p><img alt="Open installer package"
            src="images/03-10.12-keyboard-installer-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>The installer will start:
            <p><img alt="Start installation"
            src="images/04-10.12-installer-start-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>Some installers will contain information about the keyboard(s):
            <p><img alt="Installer Readme"
            src="images/05-10.12-installer-readme-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>You are ready to install:
            <p><img alt="Ready to install"
            src="images/06-10.12-installation-type-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>Installation requires administrator privileges:
            <p><img alt="Administrator privileges required"
            src="images/07-10.12-installer-admin-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>Installation is done:
            <p><img alt="Installation done"
            src="images/08-10.12-installer-done-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section>
        <title>Enabling</title>
        <p>After installation you still need to enable the new keyboard(s) to be
        able to use it/them. Do as follows:</p>
  
        <ol>
          <li>Rïhpesth <strong>Systemvalg…</strong> via the Apple menu:
            <p><img alt="Åpne &quot;Systemvalg…&quot;"
            src="images/20-10.12-systempref_menu-nob.png" /></p>
            Or via the Dock:
            <p><img alt="Åpne &quot;Systemvalg…&quot;"
            src="images/20-10.12-systempref_dock-eng.png" /></p>
          </li>

          <li>Diedtieh <strong>Tastatur</strong> jallh tjaelieh dam maam ohtsh
            daase:
            <p><img alt="Systemvalg…"
            src="images/21-10.12-systempref-nob.png" /></p>
          </li>

          <li>Diedtieh <strong>Inndatametoder</strong> jïh diedtieh dam
            pluss-væhtam mij lea vuelnie dennie gårroeh kroenesne:
            <p><img alt="Legge til samisk tastatur"
            src="images/22-10.12-systempref_input_method-nob.png" /><br/>
            Ensure that the <strong>Show Input menu in menu bar</strong> check
            box is checked.</p>
          </li>

          <li>Veeljh dam båaloebuertiem maam sïjhth jïh dle diedtieh
            <strong>Legg til</strong>:
            <p><img alt="Legge til samisk tastatur"
            src="images/23-10.12-systempref_add_keyboard-nob.png" /></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section>
        <title>Switching keyboards</title>
        <p>Minngiegeatjan dle veeljh dam saemien båaloebuertiem, gosse saemien
        tjaeledh:</p>

        <p><img alt="Velg samisk tastatur for skriving"
        src="images/30-10.12-keyboard_menu-nob.png" /></p>

        <p>JIs edtjh sneehpeslaakan båaloebuertieh målsodh, dle maahtah daejtie
        nuhtjedh <strong>Ctrl-gaskoe (⌃-␣ )</strong>.</p>
      </section>

   </body>
